Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Melbourne Strip Retail Investments and CBRE Victorian Retail Investments in conjunction with Prentice Real Estate are pleased to present to the market for sale 26-36 Ocean Beach Road, Sorrento, as part of the Peninsula Cinemas Portfolio. The property is for sale via expressions of interest closing Thursday 12th October at 5PM.

We highlight some key points below:

- 1,446sqm* of building area positioned on an irreplaceable 1,120sqm* landholding with convenient rear lane access

- 10 year lease to Peninsula Cinemas plus additional income from restaurant Acquolina, ATMs leased to Westpac and ANZ and a lease for part of the level 1 office

- Total net income of $235,186 per annum* with annual rental increases

- Exceptional exposure to Ocean Beach Road with over 30 metres* of valuable frontage

- Located in the affluent and highly sought after beachside suburb, Sorrento
